    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior presents well with a solid finish, though you may find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only modest wear on the driver's seat bolster and primary touchpoints. Mechanically, it is sound and drives beautifully, with all major systems functioning as intended and a documented service history. It\u2019s a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
      "price": 34000.0,
