      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3, a definitive example of the E46 chassis. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a meticulously serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory variable M-differential lock. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of this platform. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with all bushings and dampers providing the communicative, analog feedback the M-division is renowned for. Finished in Titanium Silver over Imola Red Nappa leather, this vehicle is a turnkey mechanical masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
